H0.text: What was the first name of the Dutch explorer, Tasman, after whom Tasmania is named. Willem

H1.text: What was the first name of the Dutch explorer, Tasman, after whom Tasmania is named. Hendrik

H2.text: What was the first name of the Dutch explorer, Tasman, after whom Tasmania is named. Cornelis

H3.text: What was the first name of the Dutch explorer, Tasman, after whom Tasmania is named. ABEL

A4.text: Abel Janszoon Tasman was a Dutch seafarer and explorer, best known for his voyages of 1642 and 1644 in the service of the Dutch East India Company (VOC).
